To build this project (not on Windows - ask Fluffy about Windows)

You might need to run autoconf, but probably not

To get a list of the accepted options, 
% ./configure --help

For shared libraries and use of distcc (for compiling across a cluster)
% ./configure --with-distcc --with-shared-libs

The default is to build static libs with no use of distcc


The default is to build with full debugging turned on. 
To build optimized, with optimization level 2, -O2: 

% make CODE_OPTIMIZE=2

